---
title: Soy-Hoisin, Lime and Sesame Chicken with Asian Summer Slaw
description: Butterflying chicken in this dish helps to keep the chicken moist while infusing it with the hoisin marinade. Topping it off with a tangy and sweet carrot, kale and kohlrabi slaw.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soy-hoisin-lime-and-sesame-chicken-7d8210a5.jpg
